description: This BONUS, EXTRA, weekend update is brought to you by a technical error that made us to stop short of a full update. So I decided to show you what we got as an EXTRA update. Dana is the real deal, shy, curious, and a total princess. She didn't know how to act, and she dealt with pain, and humiliation by laughing. I figured out early you just need to gag her! I was just getting to understand her, and what I could get out of her when we had to stop the shoot. Look for Dana again in 2 weeks, without the technical problems :)
title: Dana DeArmond
